title: Bonus Episode – Listener Q&A
description:
June 28, 2018 / Susan, Rabia and Colin take listener questions and give updates on some of the cases covered by Undisclosed. 

Episode scoring music by Blue Dot Sessions, Patrick Cortes, and Chris Zabriskie.

This episode was sponsored by Blue Apron.
